<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="fr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Nouvel avis client à valider</title>

    <style>
      body {
          font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
          line-height: 1.6;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 0;
          background-color: #f6f9fc;
          color: #32325d;
      }
      .container {
          max-width: 680px;
          margin: 40px auto;
          background-color: white;
          border-radius: 8px;
          overflow: hidden;
      }
      .header {
          background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
          color: white;
          padding: 32px;
          text-align: center;
      }
      .header h1 {
          margin: 0;
          font-size: 24px;
          font-weight: 500;
      }
      .header .order-id {
          margin-top: 8px;
          font-size: 14px;
          opacity: 0.9;
      }
      .content {
          padding: 32px;
      }
      .alert-box {
          background-color: #fff8e1;
          border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
          padding: 16px;
          margin-bottom: 32px;
          border-radius: 4px;
          font-weight: 500;
      }
      .section {
          margin-bottom: 32px;
          padding-bottom: 24px;
          border-bottom: 1px solid #e6ebf1;
      }
      .section:last-child {
          border-bottom: none;
          padding-bottom: 0;
          margin-bottom: 0;
      }
      .section-title {
          font-size: 12px;
          font-weight: 600;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          letter-spacing: 0.5px;
          color: #8898aa;
          margin-bottom: 16px;
      }
      .info-grid {
          display: table;
          width: 100%;
      }
      .info-row {
          display: table-row;
      }
      .info-label,
      .info-value {
          display: table-cell;
          padding: 8px 0;
          font-size: 15px;
      }
      .info-label {
          color: #8898aa;
          width: 40%;
      }
      .info-value {
          color: #32325d;
          font-weight: 500;
      }
      .stars {
          color: #ffc107;
          font-size: 20px;
      }
      .comment-box {
          background-color: #f6f9fc;
          border-radius: 4px;
          padding: 16px;
          margin-top: 16px;
          font-style: italic;
          color: #525f7f;
      }
      .footer {
          background-color: #f6f9fc;
          padding: 24px 32px;
          text-align: center;
          font-size: 13px;
          color: #8898aa;
      }
  </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Nouvel avis client à valider</h1>
        <div class="order-id">Commande #<%= @order_number %></div>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <div class="alert-box">
          Cet avis doit être validé avant d'être publié
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <div class="section-title">Client</div>

          <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-row">
              <div class="info-label">Nom</div>
              <div class="info-value"><%= @client_name %></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <div class="section-title">Avis</div>

          <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-row">
              <div class="info-label">Note</div>

              <div class="info-value">
                <span class="stars"><%= "★" * @rating.to_i %><%= "☆" * (5 - @rating.to_i) %></span>
                (<%= @rating %>/5)
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="comment-box"><%= @comment %></div>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
          <div class="section-title">Action requise</div>
          <p>Rendez-vous sur le dashboard pour valider ou refuser cet avis.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        Notification automatique pour l'avis de la commande
        #<%= @order_number %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
